{"tid":306094,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"飛機降落個頭痛到就黎爆","createTime":"2017-07-02T08:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T09:48:25.000Z","uid":81128,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8788828c956512ed77d3c2bacbcf6cbe8c91aa19","tid":306094,"uid":81128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:48:53.000Z","msg":"左後腦   大約耳仔垂直對上3cm左右  再往後腦2cm左右既位置 劇痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個種痛既感覺係 由入面發出 痛到用手渣住個腦<br />\n有食藥減輕個痛楚 但係訓醒 又黎過 變左每日例行食完早餐就食藥止痛<br />\n結果成個旅程我痛左2日 超過48小時 第3日訓醒先好返<br />\n<br />\n上網GOOGLE d人話係右腦痛 仲要好快好返 都係痛幾粒鐘<br />\n但係我係左後腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有幾日<br />\n第一次去旅行就咁 <br />\n已經有陰影 連旅行都唔想再去 黎緊仲有回程機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c35c5c7aae260cc6307063835f54ee9a8ee94bc3","tid":306094,"uid":15620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:51:16.000Z","msg":"連登個個都係腦科醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ae898924ad00021b9d1aced2e84e868a9dcf71","tid":306094,"uid":120581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:53:33.000Z","msg":"我都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6570a8aac6eea4b44c65a5a8571337f6d767e41b","tid":306094,"uid":31108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:58:08.000Z","msg":"係咪有感冒上機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次病住上機<br />\n對耳仔就會谷到就爆就爆咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af3f4421ae79bcc0e0a15b7c8c96422ceb6db08","tid":306094,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:58:45.000Z","msg":"鼻塞就會"},{"pid":"79d89bc59df564cf8392e4a675ea899646a92aab","tid":306094,"uid":81128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:02:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪有感冒上機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次病住上機<br />\n對耳仔就會谷到就爆就爆咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗應該就無 無流鼻水 無打乞痴<br />\n坐飛機前 對上一次訓覺係14小時前"},{"pid":"4599393865168874b2be0accb5fcd186d7a6ac33","tid":306094,"uid":81128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鼻塞就會</blockquote><br />\n我已經不停打喊路 同 吞口水"},{"pid":"a1d99e89c4650612804cbe164e7022f66e9f1d60","tid":306094,"uid":50216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:04:22.000Z","msg":"細個第一次搭飛機試過<br />\n但之後無了"},{"pid":"ed815dc57e8b401078eb3bb4f4cba703a18345d7","tid":306094,"uid":36287,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:05:30.000Z","msg":"氣壓性中耳炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我當年都有<br />\n話因為耳咽管太直搞到咁<br />\n後尾醫生教上機落機前食感冒藥就冇事<br />\n不過你點都去check下好既"},{"pid":"09cdc3844501b5e16954f2440d6f340967253c24","tid":306094,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:07:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪有感冒上機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次病住上機<br />\n對耳仔就會谷到就爆就爆咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常會「練」住個鼻谷氣<br />\n會泵到個耳仔有好似通咗下嘅感覺<br />\n快見效過吞口水/哨香口膠好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6af16175cc6445c993bcc817551a3dc992f21bf","tid":306094,"uid":66714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:09:59.000Z","msg":"通常唔夠訓就會咁 越唔夠越辛苦"},{"pid":"03d3dd861784d8f9c9934079f9137571d58a9555","tid":306094,"uid":66954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"要喺feel到耳仔塞時做減壓動作<br />\n用手指鍊住個鼻，大力噴氣，隻耳仔會卜一<br />\n聲通咗<br />\n(真係要大力噴先得，d氣喺個鼻走唔到就會去咗耳仔)<br />\n<br />\n阿媽第一次坐飛機耳仔痛，回程果時上網睇到呢個方法，之後無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb001f995c1af7e1a21256f5665363146e01ada2","tid":306094,"uid":5181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:16:05.000Z","msg":"搭咁多次耳仔都痛到仆街 食香口膠可以減輕少少<br />\n但落左機就無事<br />\n成世人唯一有一次無事就係搭airbus仲要坐中間 降落果陣舒服到仆街<br />\n拎定出黎既香口膠都唔洗食<br />\n其實關唔關架機事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98aed445e2226207a1801fcd94acf158b403c67f","tid":306094,"uid":6663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:26:03.000Z","msg":"我上次係左眼角上少少痛 隻眼痛撚到流晒眼水<br />\n<br />\n不過我估係帶con <br />\n我知我on9左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfe3e09c087e839f5753df955224d22bd6574df","tid":306094,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:26:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭咁多次耳仔都痛到仆街 食香口膠可以減輕少少<br />\n但落左機就無事<br />\n成世人唯一有一次無事就係搭airbus仲要坐中間 降落果陣舒服到仆街<br />\n拎定出黎既香口膠都唔洗食<br />\n其實關唔關架機事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有一定關係，架機細氣壓一定大D"},{"pid":"9eaeb5b4557e2b73bc4893f540082642f4aac6f1","tid":306094,"uid":81128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:27:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要喺feel到耳仔塞時做減壓動作<br />\n用手指鍊住個鼻，大力噴氣，隻耳仔會卜一<br />\n聲通咗<br />\n(真係要大力噴先得，d氣喺個鼻走唔到就會去咗耳仔)<br />\n<br />\n阿媽第一次坐飛機耳仔痛，回程果時上網睇到呢個方法，之後無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係耳仔痛 隨便吞口水, 打喊路 就會通返"},{"pid":"24683d295220b4268c7165bcfb527e6e7e96d12c","tid":306094,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:27:33.000Z","msg":"最勁𠴱次試過落機後對耳塞左成四日先冇事，期間好似聾左咁。"},{"pid":"51308eec8e64e5e9e1e69409d02b99da170bd258","tid":306094,"uid":81128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:28:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搭咁多次耳仔都痛到仆街 食香口膠可以減輕少少<br />\n但落左機就無事<br />\n成世人唯一有一次無事就係搭airbus仲要坐中間 降落果陣舒服到仆街<br />\n拎定出黎既香口膠都唔洗食<br />\n其實關唔關架機事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有一定關係，架機細氣壓一定大D</blockquote><br />\n坐平機  d位好密又窄又多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70fb2070cc1a972836bc15b0f75adc34553edc88","tid":306094,"uid":26286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:30:00.000Z","msg":"我偶爾會，有次試過痛到喊，宜家上機前一定會食止痛藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   另外就係每次搭飛機隻耳仔會塞至少半日"},{"pid":"9abcdbf84a384f2a4e9d8edc699e5a91244befbe","tid":306094,"uid":125703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:41:36.000Z","msg":"我試過一次搭細機降落香港時，個後腦劇痛，痛到好似有個炸彈係頭就黎爆，降落完一陣就無事。<br />\n<br />\n有咁既問題代唔代表身體有問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我問過同機其他朋友都無事。"},{"pid":"9e80924c557c17110154dd81b0c39b5c26992937","tid":306094,"uid":35908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:45:04.000Z","msg":"lm 我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326ea4a6fa3b20fa4080e8d818fc39290df02586","tid":306094,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T09:48:25.000Z","msg":"鏈住鼻孔合埋口,然後大力噴氣,記住係噴！之後耳仔通返就會好,之前都係咁勁痛,用完呢個方法就無事"}]}